A DNA packaging complex comprised of approximately 200 base pairs of DNA wound around a protein core, which is formed by an octomer of histones. The histone octomer includes two dimers of histones H2A and H2B that surround a tetramer consisting of two molecules of histone H3 and two molecules of histone H4.
